st\"\n```\n\nMore info: [Writing](https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html)\n\n### Run server\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo server\n```\n\nMore info: [Server](https://hexo.io/docs/server.html)\n\n### Generate static files\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo generate\n```\n\nMore info: [Generating](https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html)\n\n### Deploy to remote sites\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo deploy\n```\n\nMore info: [Deployment](https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html)\n","source":"_posts/hello-world.md","raw":"---\ntitle: Hello World\ntags: NO'1\n---\nWelcome to [Hexo](https://hexo.io/)! This is your very first post. Check [documentation](https://hexo.io/docs/) for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in [troubleshooting](https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html) or you can ask me on [GitHub](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues).\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### Create a new post\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo new \"My New Post\"\n```\n\nMore info: [Writing](https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html)\n\n### Run server\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo server\n```\n\nMore info: [Server](https://hexo.io/docs/server.html)\n\n### Generate static files\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo generate\n```\n\nMore info: [Generating](https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html)\n\n### Deploy to remote sites\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo deploy\n```\n\nMore info: [Deployment](https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html)\n","slug":"hello-world","published":1,"date":"2023-08-17T12:11:14.535Z","updated":"2023-08-17T15:51:04.105Z","_id":"cllfb5gqj0001eguadang9vey","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n","site":{"data":{}},"excerpt":"","more":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n"},{"title":"Hexo博客新建文章并发布","date":"2020-07-21T09:26:44.000Z","_content":"\n* 在git bash中输入 hexo g (完整命令为hexo generate)，用于生成静态文件\n* 再输入hexo s(完整命令为hexo server)，在本地localhost:4000中预览（这个可以省略）\n* 输入hexo d(hexo deploy)发布到git仓库上","source":"_posts/Hexo博客新建文章并发布.md","raw":"---\ntitle: Hexo博客新建文章并发布\ndate: 2020-7-21 17:26:44\ntags: Hexo\ncategories: Hexo\n---\n\n* 在git bash中输入 hexo g (完整命令为hexo generate)，用于生成静态文件\n* 再输入hexo s(完整命令为hexo server)，在本地localhost:4000中预览（这个可以省略）\n* 输入hexo d(hexo deploy)发布到git仓库上","slug":"Hexo博客新建文章并发布","published":1,"updated":"2023-08-17T15:40:05.591Z","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","_id":"cllfd6vki0000p0ua13kbc454","content":"<ul>\n<li>在git bash中输入 hexo g (完整命令为hexo generate)，用于生成静态文件</li>\n<li>再输入hexo s(完整命令为hexo server)，在本地localhost:4000中预览（这个可以省略）</li>\n<li>输入hexo d(hexo deploy)发布到git仓库上</li>\n</ul>\n","site":{"data":{}},"excerpt":"","more":"<ul>\n<li>在git bash中输入 hexo g (完整命令为hexo generate)，用于生成静态文件</li>\n<li>再输入hexo s(完整命令为hexo server)，在本地localhost:4000中预览（这个可以省略）</li>\n<li>输入hexo d(hexo deploy)发布到git仓库上</li>\n</ul>\n"},{"title":"git","date":"2023-08-17T15:03:21.000Z","_content":"\n# 在博客根目录下执行如下命令\n* 备份\n$ git add .\n$ git commit -m \"备份\"\n$ git push origin hexo\n\n* 更新\nhexo clean\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"备份\"\ngit push\nhexo g\nhexo d\n\n* 恢复\n$ git clone 仓库地址\n$ npm install hexo-cli\n$ npm install\n$ npm install hexo-deployer-git\n\n* 一键部署（博客根目录创建一个deploy.sh的文件，写入）\necho \"Start\"\nhexo clean\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"备份\"\ngit push\nhexo generate\nhexo deploy\necho \"Finish\"\necho 按任意键继续\nread -n 1  \n","source":"_posts/git.md","raw":"---\ntitle: git\ndate: 2023-08-17 23:03:21\ntags: git\n---\n\n# 在博客根目录下执行如下命令\n* 备份\n$ git add .\n$ git commit -m \"备份\"\n$ git push origin hexo\n\n* 更新\nhexo clean\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"备份\"\ngit push\nhexo g\nhexo d\n\n* 恢复\n$ git clone 仓库地址\n$ npm install hexo-cli\n$ npm install\n$ npm install hexo-deployer-git\n\n* 一键部署（博客根目录创建一个deploy.sh的文件，写入）\necho \"Start\"\nhexo clean\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"备份\"\ngit push\nhexo generate\nhexo deploy\necho \"Finish\"\necho 按任意键继续\nread -n 1  \n","slug":"git","published":1,"updated":"2023-08-18T05:27:06.315Z","_id":"cllfd6vkp0001p0uad6gq89z1","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","content":"<h1 id=\"在博客根目录下执行如下命令\"><a href=\"#在博客根目录下执行如下命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在博客根目录下执行如下命令\"></a>在博客根目录下执行如下命令</h1><ul>\n<li><p>备份<br>$ git add .<br>$ git commit -m “备份”<br>$ git push origin hexo</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>更新<br>hexo clean<br>git add .<br>git commit -m “备份”<br>git push<br>hexo g<br>hexo d</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>恢复<br>$ git clone 仓库地址<br>$ npm install hexo-cli<br>$ npm install<br>$ npm install hexo-deployer-git</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>一键部署（博客根目录创建一个deploy.sh的文件，写入）<br>echo “Start”<br>hexo clean<br>git add .<br>git commit -m “备份”<br>git push<br>hexo generate<br>hexo deploy<br>echo “Finish”<br>echo 按任意键继续<br>read -n 1</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","site":{"data":{}},"excerpt":"","more":"<h1 id=\"在博客根目录下执行如下命令\"><a href=\"#在博客根目录下执行如下命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在博客根目录下执行如下命令\"></a>在博客根目录下执行如下命令</h1><ul>\n<li><p>备份<br>$ git add .<br>$ git commit -m “备份”<br>$ git push origin hexo</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>更新<br>hexo clean<br>git add .<br>git commit -m “备份”<br>git push<br>hexo g<br>hexo d</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>恢复<br>$ git clone 仓库地址<br>$ npm install hexo-cli<br>$ npm install<br>$ npm install hexo-deployer-git</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>一键部署（博客根目录创建一个deploy.sh的文件，写入）<br>echo “Start”<br>hexo clean<br>git add .<br>git commit -m “备份”<br>git push<br>hexo generate<br>hexo deploy<br>echo “Finish”<br>echo 按任意键继续<br>read -n 1</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"},{"title":"流量卡","date":"2023-08-18T06:09:15.000Z","_content":"\n* 扫描二维码\n     ![](流量卡/ka.jpg)\n* https://haokawx.lot-ml.com/Product/Index/93535\n* 移